PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Headphone Trading Platform
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the headphone trading process work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our platform connects headphone buyers and sellers. List your headphones, browse available items, negotiate prices, and complete secure transactions through our user-friendly interface.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What types of headphones can I trade on this platform?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We welcome all types of headphones, including over-ear, on-ear, in-ear, wireless, noise-cancelling, and audiophile-grade models from various brands.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How do you ensure the quality of traded headphones?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Sellers are required to provide detailed descriptions and photos. We also have a user rating system and encourage buyers to leave honest reviews after each transaction.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if I'm not satisfied with my purchase?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We offer a 7-day return policy for most transactions. If you encounter any issues, our customer support team is ready to assist you in resolving the matter.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our headphone trading marketplace
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the headphone trading process work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our platform allows users to list, buy, and sell headphones. After creating an account, you can list your headphones for sale or browse available listings. Once a deal is agreed upon, we facilitate the secure transaction and shipping process.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What types of headphones can I trade on this platform?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We accept all types of headphones, including over-ear, on-ear, in-ear, wireless, and wired models from various brands. Both new and used headphones in good condition are welcome on our marketplace.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How is the authenticity of headphones verified?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We have a team of experts who review listings and can perform authenticity checks on high-value items. We also encourage sellers to provide detailed photos and documentation. Buyers are protected by our money-back guarantee if they receive counterfeit products.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: What fees are associated with using the platform?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: We charge a small commission on successful sales, typically around 5-10% depending on the item's value. Listing items is free, and buyers don't pay any additional fees beyond the purchase price and shipping costs.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How are disputes between buyers and sellers handled?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We have a dedicated customer support team that mediates disputes. If an issue arises, both parties can open a case, provide evidence, and our team will work to find a fair resolution. We aim to protect both buyers and sellers throughout the trading process.
